![diagram](https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4D22AQHrovWhJxGrsQ/feedshare-shrink_800/feedshare-shrink_800/0/1695616779243?e=2147483647&amp;v=beta&amp;t=dZNazAKryQW6nNz6qjlu-YWcJpNirlOJdYyr-DfOZbs)
